Garden Bloom is a soft, literary AO3 site skin built on a palette of sage green, warm blush pink, and cream white — like a garden in early morning light. Tag pills are colour-coded by type, fic titles appear in warm amber italic, and the header carries the site name in Cinzel with a pink-to-forest gradient. The sidebar uses a dashed sage border, buttons are a quiet translucent sage tint, and the footer is a flat near-black with a blush top stripe. Body text is set in Crimson Pro for comfortable long-form reading.
